How to configure:
==============

Edit the IP in client.py to your server's address.

How to run:
==========

First run the server. 
Enter the file to be sent
Enter the port number(eg.3333)

Now run the client
Enter the file to be saved as
Enter the port number of the server
Wait..

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

How to compile:
==============

gcc client.c -o client
gcc server.c -o server

How to run:
==========

Run each command on a different terminal window

./client hostname portno
./server portno

Note: Start the server first and then the client.

Sample:
./server 1234
./client ubuntu 1234



